00:21:42.367 --> 00:21:45.467
the very max and the very min,
but I tried to take an average

00:21:45.467 --> 00:21:48.133
of the minimum and kind
of a general value

00:21:48.133 --> 00:21:49.133
for the higher ones.

00:21:49.133 --> 00:21:50.933
I didn't push it to the limit.

00:21:50.933 --> 00:21:52.233
You can't read that
scale there.

00:21:52.233 --> 00:21:55.200
But that would be slightly
